OL,3,CFamilies of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Cto meet Prime Minister next week
OL,6,FThe families of the Nottingham attacks
OL,7,Fvictims have announced that they will
OL,8,Fmeet the Prime Minister in their push
OL,9,Ffor an urgent statutory Judge led
OL,10,Fpublic inquiry into the triple killing.
OL,12,FValdo Calocane, who had been diagnosed
OL,13,Fwith paranoid schizophrenia, was
OL,14,Fsentenced to an indefinite hospital
OL,15,Forder after killing 19-year-old
OL,16,Fstudents Barnaby Webber, Grace
OL,17,FO'Malley-Kumar and 65-year-old
OL,18,Fcaretaker Ian Coates in June 2023.
