OL,3,CFamilies of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Cto meet Prime Minister next week
OL,6,FThe knifeman also attempted to kill
OL,7,Fthree other people in the spate of
OL,8,Fattacks in Nottingham.
OL,10,FThe families will now have a face-to-
OL,11,Fface meeting with Sir Kier Starmer
OL,12,Fnext Wednesday (February 12th).
OL,14,FIt follows the publication this week
OL,15,Fof a damning independent review
OL,16,Fcommissioned by NHS England of the
OL,17,Fmultiple failings by mental health
OL,18,Fservices in Nottinghamshire and by
OL,19,Fpolice in the run-up to fatal attacks
OL,20,Fin June 2023.
