OL,6,FThe review said other patients cared
OL,7,Ffor by Nottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust also committed
OL,9,F"extremely serious" acts of violence `
OL,10,Fincluding stabbings ` between 2019 and
OL,11,F2023.
OL,13,FThe NHS took the decision to publish
OL,14,Fthe report in full after originally
OL,15,Fsaying that only a redacted version
OL,16,Fwould be released because of
OL,17,F"protection legislation relating to
OL,18,Fpatient information".
