OL,6,FDr Jessica Sokolov, regional medical
OL,7,Fdirector at NHS England (Midlands),
OL,8,Fsaid: "It's clear the system got it
OL,9,Fwrong, including the NHS, and the
OL,10,Fconsequences of when this happens can
OL,11,Fbe devastating.
OL,13,F"This is not acceptable, and I
OL,14,Funreservedly apologise to the families
OL,15,Fof victims on behalf of the NHS and
OL,16,Fthe organisations involved in
OL,17,Fdelivering care to Valdo Calocane
OL,18,Fbefore this incident took place."
