OL,6,FClaire Murdoch, NHS England's national
OL,7,Fmental health director, said: "It is
OL,8,Fclear there were failings in the care
OL,9,Fprovided to Valdo Calocane, which is
OL,10,Fwhy the trust responsible was placed
OL,11,Fin our highest oversight and support
OL,12,Fprogramme, which has seen them
OL,13,Foverhaul their risk assessment
OL,14,Fprocesses.
